Nicholas Thomas "Nicky" Walker (born 8 September 1994) is an English semi-professional footballer who plays as a winger for National League North side Alfreton Town.
He has previously played for Rotherham United, Barrow, Wycombe Wanderers, Grimsby Town and Shaw Lane.
